message: A smile is a light in the window of your face to show your heart is at home.
title: Thought of the day

author: Byron Pulsifer
message: Look forward to spring as a time when you can start to see what nature has to offer once again.
title: Thought of the day

author: Billy Wilder
message: Trust your own instinct. Your mistakes might as well be your own, instead of someone elses.
title: Thought of the day

author: Blaise Pascal
message: The least movement is of importance to all nature. The entire ocean is affected by a pebble.
title: Thought of the day
